title: Episode 17: Skye Reedy
description:
On today's episode, Kailey sits down and catches up with one of her longtime Nashville friends and Christian  recording artist, Skye Reedy! While Skye and Kailey  reminisce on the early years of their friendship, Skye  also shares about her intimate relationship with God and  how He faithfully brought her inner healing from past  trauma, loss and grief.

Stream Skye Reedy's song: Reconcile
